    <body>
        <p>You can pin your favorite styles to keep them displayed at the top of the list. This can be done in the following places in Flare:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Styles Window Pane (<span class="Emphasis">F12</span>)</li>
            <li>Styles Drop-Down Field (<span class="Emphasis">Home Ribbon</span>)</li>
            <li>Floating Style Picker (<span class="Emphasis">CTRL+SHIFT+H</span>)</li>
        </ul>
        <p MadCap:conditions="General.OnlineLive">For more information about these three locations, see <MadCap:xref href="../../../Styles/Applying_Styles_to_Content.htm">Applying Styles to Content</MadCap:xref>.</p>
        <p>
            <img src="../../Images/pin_styles1.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth60Percent" />
        </p>
        <MadCap:snippetBlock src="../EmptyPageBreakAfter.flsnp" MadCap:conditions="FlareGuides.FlareStylesGuide" />
        <p>To pin a style, hover over the style row and click the little pin. It will then be moved to the top of the list. </p>
        <p>
            <img src="../../Images/pin_styles2.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth90Percent" />
        </p>
        <MadCap:snippetBlock src="../EmptyPageBreakAfter.flsnp" MadCap:conditions="FlareGuides.FlareStylesGuide,FlareGuides.FlareWhatsNewGuide" />
        <p>To unpin a style, just click the pin again and it will be moved back to the bottom section of the list.</p>
        <p>
            <img src="../../Images/pin_styles3.png" alt="" title="" class="MaxWidth100Percent" />
        </p>
    </body>
</html>